title: [Endeltime Estates, The Passing]
description: A rusted iron gate dominates the open, dirt-packed road, its bars bent and broken beneath the wrought metal raven adorning the top, its gilt-pronged eye sockets gouged by heavy vines piercing through the available space.  The crumbling facades surrounding the gate cast ominous shadows through the broken windows, each one marked by a faded blood red sigil.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
